### ===========================================
### 13. 课程表全量接口
### ===========================================

### 13.1 获取课表绑定次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/coursetable/bind-count
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 13.2 更新用户班级
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/coursetable/class
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "class_id": "2023级软件工程1班"
}

### 13.3 编辑课表单元格
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/coursetable/
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "semester": "2024-2025-1",
  "index": "1",
  "value": {
    "course_name": "高等数学",
    "teacher": "张老师",
    "location": "主教A101"
  }
}

### 13.4 重置个人课表
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/coursetable/schedule?semester=2024-2025-1
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 13.5 管理员重置用户绑定次数
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/coursetable/reset/{{targetUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

