Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14.2 创建英雄
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/heroes/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试英雄",
  "sort": 100,
  "is_show": true
}

### 14.3 更新英雄
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/heroes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试英雄-更新",
  "sort": 101,
  "is_show": true
}

### 14.4 删除英雄
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/heroes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14.5 公开获取配置
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/config/test_key

### 14.6 管理员搜索配置
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/config/search?query=&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14.7 创建配置
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/config/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

