PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/config/test.feature.flag
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "disabled",
  "value_type": "string",
  "description": "更新后的测试配置"
}

### 14.9 删除配置
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/config/test.feature.flag
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ===========================================
### 15. 存储接口
### ===========================================

### 15.1 上传文件
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=GoJxustBoundary

--GoJxustBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

hello gojxust
--GoJxustBoundary--

### 15.2 获取文件列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store/list
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 15.3 获取过期文件列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store/expired
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 15.4 获取文件下载 URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store/{{resourceId}}/url?expires=3600&download=false
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 15.5 获取文件流
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store/{{resourceId}}/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 15.6 删除文件
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/store/{{resourceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

