### ===========================================
### 19. 资料接口
### ===========================================

### 19.1 获取资料列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/?page=1&page_size=10&sort_by=hotness
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.2 获取热门资料
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/top?limit=10&type=7
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.3 获取热词
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/hot-words?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.4 搜索资料
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/search?keywords=高数&page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.5 获取资料详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/{{materialMd5}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.6 资料评分
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/{{materialMd5}}/rating
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5
}

### 19.7 下载资料
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/materials/{{materialMd5}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.8 获取资料分类列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/material-categories/
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 19.9 管理员删除资料
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/materials/{{materialMd5}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 19.10 管理员更新资料描述
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/material-desc/{{materialMd5}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": "高数,期末",
  "description": "更新后的资料描述",
  "external_link": "https://example.com/material",
  "is_recommended": true
}

### ===========================================
### 20. 通知与分类完整接口
### ===========================================

### 20.1 获取通知列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/notifications/?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 20.2 获取通知详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 20.3 获取分类列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/categories/
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 20.4 管理员通知列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.5 管理员通知统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.6 管理员通知详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.7 创建通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试通知",
  "content": "这是一条测试通知",
  "categories": [{{categoryId}}]
}

### 20.8 更新通知
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试通知-更新",
  "content": "更新后的通知内容",
  "categories": [{{categoryId}}]
}

### 20.9 发布通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.10 审核通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1,
  "note": "审核通过"
}

### 20.11 转换为日程
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "考试安排",
  "description": "来自通知的日程",
  "time_slots": [
    {
      "name": "期末考试",
      "start_date": "2026-06-20",
      "end_date": "2026-06-20",
      "start_time": "09:00",
      "end_time": "11:00",
      "is_all_day": false
    }
  ]
}

### 20.12 删除通知
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.13 管理员直接发布通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/publish-admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.14 置顶通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/pin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.15 取消置顶
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}/unpin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20.16 创建通知分类
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/categories/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试分类",
  "sort": 100,
  "is_active": true
}

### 20.17 更新通知分类
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试分类-更新",
  "sort": 101,
  "is_active": true
}

### ===========================================
### 21. 刷题、番茄钟、词典、统计
### ===========================================

### 21.1 获取项目列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/questions/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.2 获取题目 ID 列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/questions/list?project_id={{projectId}}&random=false
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.3 获取题目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/questions/{{questionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.4 记录学习次数
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/questions/study
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": {{questionId}},
  "project_id": {{projectId}}
}

### 21.5 提交做题记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/questions/practice
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": {{questionId}},
  "project_id": {{projectId}}
}

### 21.6 获取番茄钟次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/pomodoro/count
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.7 增加番茄钟次数
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/pomodoro/increment
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.8 获取番茄钟排名
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/pomodoro/ranking
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.9 获取随机单词
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/dictionary/word
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.10 获取系统在线人数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/stat/system/online
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.11 获取项目在线人数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/stat/project/{{projectId}}/online
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 21.12 获取所有启用项目在线人数（管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/stats/projects/online
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ===========================================
### 22. 聊天接口
### ===========================================

### 22.1 创建对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试对话"
}

### 22.2 获取对话列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 22.3 获取单个对话
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 22.4 更新对话
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试对话-更新"
}

### 22.5 删除对话
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 22.6 导出对话
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}/export
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}

### 22.7 流式对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/chat/conversation
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation_id": {{conversationId}},
  "message": {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "你好，帮我总结一下高数复习重点"
  }
}

### ===========================================
### 23. 功能白名单管理
### ===========================================

### 23.1 获取功能列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23.2 获取功能详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23.3 创建功能
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "feature_key": "{{featureKey}}",
  "feature_name": "测试功能",
  "description": "用于 api_test 的功能",
  "is_enabled": true
}

### 23.4 更新功能
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "feature_name": "测试功能-更新",
  "description": "更新后的描述"
}

### 23.5 获取功能白名单
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}/whitelist?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23.6 授予功能权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}/whitelist
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": {{targetUserId}}
}

### 23.7 批量授予功能权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}/whitelist/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_ids": [{{targetUserId}}]
}

### 23.8 撤销功能权限
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}/whitelist/{{targetUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23.9 查看用户功能权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/features
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23.10 删除功能
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/features/{{featureKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ===========================================
### 24. 用户管理与 RBAC
### ===========================================

### 24.1 获取用户详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.2 踢下线用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/kick
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.3 封禁用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/ban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "duration_seconds": 3600,
  "reason": "测试封禁"
}

### 24.4 解封用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/unban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.5 获取角色列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.6 获取角色及权限列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/roles/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.7 创建角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_tag": "test_role",
  "name": "测试角色",
  "description": "用于接口测试"
}

### 24.8 更新角色
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试角色-更新",
  "description": "更新后的角色描述"
}

### 24.9 获取权限列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24.10 创建权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission_tag": "test.permission",
  "name": "测试权限",
  "description": "用于接口测试"
}

### 24.11 更新角色权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission_ids": [{{permissionId1}}, {{permissionId2}}]
}

### 24.12 更新用户角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/users/{{targetUserId}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_ids": [{{roleId}}]
}

### 24.13 获取用户权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/admin/rbac/users/{{targetUserId}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ===========================================
### 25. MCP 接口
### ===========================================

### 25.1 MCP initialize
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "api_test",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### 25.2 MCP tools/call - listHeroes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp
Authorization: Bearer {{normalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "listHeroes",
    "arguments": {}
  }
}

### ===========================================
### 使用说明：
### 1. 修改 @baseUrl 为实际的服务器地址
### 2. 先执行模拟登录接口获取token
### 3. 将获取的token复制到 @normalToken 或 @adminToken 变量中
### 4. 按需执行各个测试用例
### 5. 观察响应结果，验证API功能是否正常
### ===========================================
